{"type":null,"faqId":45328,"title":"荣耀盒子M321播放外部存储设备（如移动硬盘、U盘、microSD卡）上的视频卡顿，怎么办？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\r\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\r\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>\"1. 可能是您的存储设备（U 盘、microSD 卡）读取速度过慢，未达到视频文件的码流速率。请换另一个存储设备试试。<br>\n2. 请使用第三方播放器（如 XBMC、Mx Player）播放试试。<br>\n3. 如果仍有问题，且在其他设备或播放器上播放顺畅。请致电华为客服并将视频传送给我们。我们将为您解决。<br>\n4. 可能是您的视频文件不标准，请尝试更换为标准的视频文件。盒子支持的格式有：AVI、RM、RMVB、MKV、TS、MPEG、MP4、MOV、VOB、WMV、DAT等。\" <br>\n</span></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":244,"faqType":"在线播放","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"849","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Online-Play","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556873000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":5,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"外部设备,卡顿,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}